{"sections":{"6d643e57-958f-4776-a094-974a2e5f549d":{"type":"three-column","blocks":{"template--16110884159657__6d643e57-958f-4776-a094-974a2e5f549d-16825734164b96972c-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Screenshot_2023-02-23_at_4.37.40_pm.png"}}},"block_order":["template--16110884159657__6d643e57-958f-4776-a094-974a2e5f549d-16825734164b96972c-0"],"settings":{"enable_dark":false,"subheading":"<p><strong>IMPACT<\/strong><\/p>","title":"<p>Our NMJ <em>Community<\/em><\/p>","description":"<p>We harness unimaginable strength when we move together. Determined to affect social and environmental change, we collaborate with organisations, charities and artists that enrich and nourish lives; bringing hope and opportunity.<\/p><p>We continually adjust our focus, paying close attention to the existing and arising challenges that are facing many across the world. When the devastating bushfires swept through Australia in 2019, we designed the Golden Wattle Pendant to raise funds for WIRES and Red Cross Australia. Our tangible symbol of hope continues to devote a percentage of proceeds to a number of charities, chosen by each customer. You can read about the Golden Wattle’s journey below.<\/p>","feature_text":"<p>Natalie Marie Jewellery has, at its heart, <em>the essence of community<\/em> and <em>family<\/em> guiding us.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_metaobject":"","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_2_metaobject":"","button_2_text":"","button_2_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"8aa0b652-00e7-4189-b615-c58dcf202e02":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16110884159657__8aa0b652-00e7-4189-b615-c58dcf202e02-1682573092e7b4910c-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Niah-x-Walawaani_1200x_copy.png"}}},"block_order":["template--16110884159657__8aa0b652-00e7-4189-b615-c58dcf202e02-1682573092e7b4910c-0"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":true,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"left","media_width":"6","content_position":"topLeftSticky","subheading":"","title":"","description":"<p>Our collaboration with artist <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/blogs\/news\/niah-mcleod\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/blogs\/news\/niah-mcleod\"><em>Niah McLeod<\/em><\/a>, culminated in the Walawaani Collection, a limited edition capsule designed to raise awareness of NAIDOC week. Funds raised through sales of the collection were donated directly to <a href=\"https:\/\/www.yalari.org\/\" target=\"_blank\"><em>Yalari<\/em><\/a>, who’s founder’s Waverley and Liew work with great heart to educate and empower Indigenous kids across Australia and the Torres Strait.<\/p>","colour_style":"dark","button_1_text":"","button_1_link":"","button_style":"underline"}},"590df56c-3713-4c25-b48b-9259be651b55":{"type":"text-with-media","blocks":{"template--16110884159657__590df56c-3713-4c25-b48b-9259be651b55-1682573092e7b4910c-0":{"type":"image","settings":{"image":"shopify:\/\/shop_images\/Bushfire-x-Golden-Wattle_header_1200x_copy.png"}}},"block_order":["template--16110884159657__590df56c-3713-4c25-b48b-9259be651b55-1682573092e7b4910c-0"],"settings":{"remove_spacing_top":true,"remove_spacing_bottom":true,"enable_newsletter_subscribe":false,"klaviyo_form_id":"","media_position":"right","media_width":"7","content_position":"topLeftSticky","subheading":"","title":"","description":"<p>2022 has already seen our collaboration with Barkindji woman, <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/blogs\/news\/meet-the-maker-lily-bennett\" target=\"_blank\" title=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/blogs\/news\/meet-the-maker-lily-bennett\"><em>Lily Bennett<\/em><\/a><em> <\/em>come to life. This partnership saw a custom artwork by Lily hand-engraved onto an <a href=\"https:\/\/www.nataliemariejewellery.com\/products\/nhurali-pendant?_pos=1&_sid=62fa365ec&_ss=r\" target=\"_blank